Authors of Byrne's Euclid — Book I Decks
========================================

Suhas Bhat  (@suhasbhat111)  — https://github.com/suhasbhat111

Developed with Claude Code (v2.1.145, Anthropic),
using Claude Opus 4.8 and Claude Sonnet 4.6.

Based on the public-domain original:
  Oliver Byrne, "The First Six Books of the Elements of Euclid" (London, 1847).

Built on (not redistributed here; install from CTAN/TeX Live):
  the `byrne` LaTeX + MetaPost package by Sergey Slyusarev (jemmybutton),
  GPL-3.0 — https://github.com/jemmybutton/byrne-latex
  and his full recreation of Byrne's Euclid — https://github.com/jemmybutton/byrne-euclid
  This project depends on his package to draw every figure and inline symbol.
